   5G-simulator RELEASE NOTES
=========================

This file contains 5G-simulator release notes
(ordered from the most recent one).

Release 18.06
=============

Availability
------------
This release is available from this git repository
        https://bitbucket.org/telematicslab/5g-simulator.git


Supported platforms
-------------------
tested on
       - Linux amd64 Ubuntu 16.04 with g++ 5.4.0

New user-visible features
-------------------------
  - MIMO transmission modes up to TM9
  - HARQ retransmissions
  - MBSFN multicast and broadcast transmission
  - SRTA-PI technique for channel estimation at high speed
  - Random access procedure
    NB-IoT functionality

